[Student "S"]
{SOUTH bids 4\C, showing \H support, 13+ points and a singleton 
or void in \Cs.

NORTH first shows her \DA, then, when SOUTH signs off, 
makes one more try by showing her \SA.

SOUTH finally gets inspired and bids the slam.}

