[Student "S"]
{WEST has a very minimum 2NT bid, but when EAST shows \C shortness she can Control-bid 
her \HA without showing extra values.

EAST's hand became huge when he heard about WEST's \HA. 
When Blackwood shows they hold three Aces he bids what he expects to be a comfortable slam.}

